column1: Baby Barnaby's////I love Barnabys. Good food that seems to have a healthier twist to it. The reason for 4 stars is they are sometimes inconsistent between locations. I got this one salad with the sumac chicken (forgot the name) but absolutely loved that it had mint in it
column2: it was so refreshing. Went to another location and ordered it and they forgot the mint :( but overall great food. The queso
column5: salads are all great. A little pricey but I feel that's just normal for going out now. Idk when 12-16$ because normal for a salad but it has happened.
